OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FBy one gauge, Eluned Morgan's route to
OL,7,Fthe top has taken her six years but by
OL,8,Fanother it's been a 30-year journey.
OL,10,FThe contrast is stark between her
OL,11,F'coronation' as Welsh Labour leader,
OL,12,Funopposed with the support of nearly
OL,13,Fevery Senedd member, and her third
OL,14,Fplace in 2018's leadership election.
