OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FIn fact she very nearly didn't even
OL,7,Fget to third place. Struggling to win
OL,8,Fenough support to be on the ballot,
OL,9,Fshe relied on the then First Minister
OL,10,FCarwyn Jones 'lending' her his
OL,11,Fnomination in order to ensure that a
OL,12,Fwoman was in the contest.
OL,14,FShe certainly wasn't seen as a likely
OL,15,Funifying figure at that stage, unlike
OL,16,Fnow.
