OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FBy that point there was no denying her
OL,7,Fexperience: her career as an elected
OL,8,Fpolitician began in 1994 when she
OL,9,Fbecame an MEP. After that, and before
OL,10,Fshe switched to Cardiff Bay, she went
OL,11,Fto the House of Lords where she was a
OL,12,FShadow Minister for much of her time.
OL,14,FBut this was the time of 'clear red
OL,15,Fwater' - emphasising policy
OL,16,Fdifferences between Welsh Labour and
OL,17,Fthe UK Labour Party as led by Tony
OL,18,FBlair and Gordon Brown.
