OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FTo a certain extent, the change that's
OL,7,Fhappened since then has been that the
OL,8,Fpolitical landscape has shifted. To be
OL,9,Fseen as a 'Blairite', as Eluned Morgan
OL,10,Fcertainly was, is no longer quite the
OL,11,Fproblem it was back then.
OL,13,FPerhaps 'clear red water' was only
OL,14,Fever possible during a time when Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment budgets were booming. Now a
OL,16,Fcloser alignment with Keir Starmer's
OL,17,Fbrand of Labour seems more likely.
