OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FEluned Morgan has also changed. Her
OL,7,Fleadership bid trumpeted her 'radical'
OL,8,Fsocialism which may have raised
OL,9,Feyebrows six years ago but not now.
OL,11,FWhat next?
OL,13,FNow she has to become First Minister
OL,14,Fand that requires a vote in the
OL,15,FSenedd. Since it's on recess, that
OL,16,Fwould mean it being recalled and that,
OL,17,Fin turn, depends on whether or not
OL,18,FVaughan Gething intends to resign his
OL,19,Fpost now or wait until the start of
OL,20,Fterm in September.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
