OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FIf, as seems likely, he tenders his
OL,7,Fresignation to the King in the next
OL,8,Fday or two, the recall could happen
OL,9,Fnext week, most likely next Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe vote, by the way, takes the form
OL,12,Fof a roll call. Each Senedd member is
OL,13,Fcalled in alphabetical order to say
OL,14,Fwho they are nominating for First
OL,15,FMinister or to abstain. When this took
OL,16,Fplace in March, Conservatives named
OL,17,Ftheir leader Andrew RT Davies while
OL,18,FPlaid Cymru MSs did the same for Rhun
OL,19,Fap Iorwerth.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
