OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FIt will mean 'pairing' or arranging
OL,7,Ffor members of different parties to
OL,8,Fcancel each other's votes. The pairing
OL,9,Fsystem failed when Vaughan Gething
OL,10,Ffaced a confidence vote, but there's a
OL,11,Fgood chance that it will hold on this
OL,12,Foccasion.
OL,14,FOnce the roll call has been held, and
OL,15,Fassuming that Eluned Morgan is chosen,
OL,16,Fthe Llywydd, Elin Jones, then writes
OL,17,Fto the King with the Senedd's
OL,18,Frecommendation.
