OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FThat's the point when Eluned Morgan
OL,7,Fbecomes the first female First
OL,8,FMinister of Wales and also the point
OL,9,Fwhen the really hard work begins.
OL,11,FThe challenges ahead
OL,13,FIt's hard to overstate the difficulty
OL,14,FWelsh Labour is facing. Its divisions
OL,15,Fare the deepest and most public that
OL,16,Fthey've been for 25 years - healing
OL,17,Fthose wounds will be a major challenge
OL,18,Ffor Eluned Morgan.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
