OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FSome within the party share some of
OL,7,Fthe feeling expressed by opposition
OL,8,Fparties, that it's been in power too
OL,9,Flong and is becoming tired and out of
OL,10,Ftouch.
OL,12,FIronically given its celebration of
OL,13,Fvictory in the UK General Election,
OL,14,FLabour in Wales is looking at some
OL,15,Fterrifying poll numbers showing it
OL,16,Fwill struggle in the next Senedd
OL,17,Felection which is due to be held in
OL,18,F2026.
