OL,3,C'A serious situation' facing Eluned
OL,4,CMorgan, the new Welsh Labour leader
OL,6,FNot only that but it will fight that
OL,7,Felection on a voting system -
OL,8,Fintroduced by itself with Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fsupport - that makes it almost
OL,10,Fimpossible for any party to gain a
OL,11,Fmajority and will give more seats to
OL,12,Fothers, including smaller parties such
OL,13,Fas Reform UK and the Green Party.
OL,15,FThere are those within Welsh Labour
OL,16,Fwho fear that disaster is looming for
OL,17,Fthem in 2026 and an unprecedented
OL,18,Fperiod of opposition will follow.
